<mj-section>
  <mj-column>
    <mj-text
      font-size="24px"
      font-weight="bold"
      color="#4a4a4a"
      align="center"
      padding-bottom="20px"
    >
      Email Verification ✅
    </mj-text>

    <mj-text> Hey {{name}}! 👋 </mj-text>

    <mj-text>
      Thanks for joining us! Just one quick step to go - verify your email address to unlock all the
      awesome features waiting for you.
    </mj-text>

    <mj-text> Just click this button to verify your email: </mj-text>

    <mj-button
      background-color="#F7B801"
      color="white"
      border-radius="4px"
      font-weight="bold"
      href="{{verificationLink}}"
    >
      Verify Email Address 🔑
    </mj-button>

    <mj-text font-size="14px"> Or copy and paste this link if you prefer: </mj-text>

    <mj-text font-size="14px" color="#F7B801" word-break="break-all">
      {{verificationLink}}
    </mj-text>

    <mj-text> This link will expire in 1 hour, so don't wait too long! ⏱️ </mj-text>

    <mj-text> If you did not create an account, you can safely ignore this email. </mj-text>
  </mj-column>
</mj-section>
